{"tid":686210,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拉莫斯及其家人受到死亡威脅","createTime":"2018-06-01T05:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T07:53:32.000Z","uid":124292,"like":63,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d3fbccb429017f8546b3b708e99170f871e92eda","tid":686210,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:00:42.000Z","msg":"科貝電台報道，皇馬後衛拉莫斯因在歐冠決賽中弄傷沙拿而處在非常複雜的情況下。<br />\n<br />\n由於很多人認為拉莫斯是故意弄沙拿，讓他退出比賽，他們在社交網絡對拉莫斯進行騷擾和攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n週一，據埃及媒體稱，事件再次升級。有1000人在開羅的西班牙大使館示威，抗議拉莫斯。<br />\n<br />\n同時，拉莫斯和他的家人開始受到死亡威脅，還有來自不明號碼的來電。這對拉莫斯和他的身邊人來說已經是一種騷擾。為此拉莫斯的家人被迫換掉了手機號碼。<br />\n<br />\n目前警方正在為拉莫斯及其家人調查這些騷擾。"},{"pid":"62bde5bfe069d342df98570318dc39d9b06d86b3","tid":686210,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734125d4b20a9488d7b4426c6a74e38459c1650f","tid":686210,"uid":34571,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:22:57.000Z","msg":"開羅果堆都係疤狗"},{"pid":"37bb4d407d196e8717982971a823a01354957b77","tid":686210,"uid":171177,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:27:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f9951af4e93e0988a127468a5fe2355a1417656","tid":686210,"uid":26232,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:33:35.000Z","msg":"蝗迷開始支持拉膠行動未"},{"pid":"e214af78294fd12565488c9dbf7d202aa7b18a98","tid":686210,"uid":171754,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:33:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9da3a9d6bbab5857184910b4071c5c3f05fdb753","tid":686210,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3abfa321bc1e6441508197b915028f1a72e7aff","tid":686210,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:36:07.000Z","msg":"佢係得罪整個回教世界"},{"pid":"ef668